1308
01:17:44,159 --> 01:17:46,695
you don't need to have a reason for that either.

1309
01:17:47,396 --> 01:17:49,197
But it is also why that walking

1310
01:17:49,231 --> 01:17:51,199
disaster of a brother of yours,

1311
01:17:51,233 --> 01:17:54,436
might show up as well without reason.

1312
01:17:54,469 --> 01:17:57,172
[Shinpachi] Kagura said Umibozu looked a little sad

1313
01:17:57,205 --> 01:18:01,209
and he left with those words, and he also looked bald.

1314
01:18:01,243 --> 01:18:03,211
[electricty whooshing]

1315
01:18:03,245 --> 01:18:05,313
