1320
01:18:14,222 --> 01:18:15,991
[Soyo] Have a look at this, everyone.

1321
01:18:16,391 --> 01:18:18,326
Can you believe how well the rebuild

1322
01:18:18,360 --> 01:18:20,095
of the Terminal is going?

1323
01:18:20,128 --> 01:18:22,931
