1324
01:18:23,131 --> 01:18:25,801
as long as we never give up, we should be able

1325
01:18:25,834 --> 01:18:29,204
to get back up and continue as many times as it takes.

1326
01:18:29,237 --> 01:18:30,372
So please, everyone--

1327
01:18:30,405 --> 01:18:32,374
Princess Soyo, I hate to interrupt,

1328
01:18:32,407 --> 01:18:34,543
