1332
01:18:41,850 --> 01:18:43,251
[upbeat music]

1333
01:18:45,420 --> 01:18:48,256
[Nobume] If you believe the princess to be the kind of person

1334
01:18:48,290 --> 01:18:50,425
to kill anyone who gets in her way,

1335
01:18:51,326 --> 01:18:53,995
