1336
01:18:54,029 --> 01:18:56,131
before her, ready to die yourselves?

1337
01:18:56,164 --> 01:18:57,399
Nobume, please.

1338
01:18:57,432 --> 01:18:58,600
It's an assassin!

1339
01:18:58,633 --> 01:19:01,036
