1342
01:19:06,541 --> 01:19:08,443
was thanks to these girls.

1343
01:19:09,044 --> 01:19:11,179
Actually, I'm sure they had on their side

1344
01:19:11,213 --> 01:19:12,848
the spirits of three great men,

1345
01:19:12,881 --> 01:19:15,016
and, well, maybe one more.

1346
