1399
01:21:20,342 --> 01:21:23,278
And that was be the last time he played the straight man.

1400
01:21:23,311 --> 01:21:25,447
- [Shinpachi] I'm not dead! - [electricity whooshing]

1401
01:21:25,680 --> 01:21:29,251
[Shinpachi] Don't worry folks, I'm not handing over the narration. Okay.

1402
01:21:29,284 --> 01:21:31,553
The Zuramp Administration handed things over

1403
01:21:31,586 --> 01:21:34,022
