1407
01:21:44,733 --> 01:21:46,067
[tense music]

1408
01:21:46,101 --> 01:21:48,136
If you are prepared to die,

1409
01:21:49,204 --> 01:21:53,208
then drink my friends, and puke!

1410
01:21:53,241 --> 01:21:54,676
[all cheering]

1411
01:21:54,709 --> 01:21:56,011
[glasses clanking]

1412
01:21:56,044 --> 01:21:57,345
[laughter]

1413
01:21:57,746 --> 01:21:58,914
[soft music]

1414
01:21:58,947 --> 01:22:01,216
[Kondo] There are no breaks in their war.

1415
01:22:02,217 --> 01:22:05,053
A life like that can be overwhelming at times,

1416
01:22:05,086 --> 01:22:07,956
