1428
01:22:38,653 --> 01:22:40,755
You can stop it, I'm standing right here.

1429
01:22:40,789 --> 01:22:43,058
And that goes for you too, Sis!

1430
01:22:43,091 --> 01:22:45,360
Why are you going along with all this nonsense?

1431
01:22:45,393 --> 01:22:48,096
