1432
01:22:48,530 --> 01:22:49,597
I was just checking in.

1433
01:22:50,231 --> 01:22:52,667
[soft music]

1434
01:22:56,338 --> 01:22:57,539
[Otae] Yo, Gorilla.

1435
01:22:58,406 --> 01:23:00,642
Didn't I say you'd have to pay triple the price

1436
01:23:00,675 --> 01:23:02,510
