1437
01:23:02,544 --> 01:23:05,280
[Shinpachi] You were saying all kinds of crazy stuff during the narration!

1438
01:23:05,680 --> 01:23:08,083
Yes, my very wallet...

1439
01:23:08,116 --> 01:23:11,753
No, the government's coffers, they belong to you now.

1440
01:23:11,786 --> 01:23:14,689
Take this, it's a B's concert ticket.

1441
01:23:15,657 --> 01:23:18,727
Well, Gorilla, you're a naughty one, aren't you?

1442
01:23:18,760 --> 01:23:20,295
Not as naughty as you are sweet.

1443
01:23:22,063 --> 01:23:22,530
[Shinpachi] This footage has become evidence of official corruption!

1444
01:23:23,331 --> 01:23:25,133
You use narration to hide it, huh?

1445
01:23:25,166 --> 01:23:27,802
Oh, come one. You ate up all that screen time.

1446
01:23:27,836 --> 01:23:28,970
And the punch-line was just that

1447
01:23:29,004 --> 01:23:31,539
you're still a bunch of idiots? You need to fix this.

1448
01:23:31,573 --> 01:23:34,709
Yes, well, no news is good news, right?

1449
01:23:35,443 --> 01:23:38,680
I don't need a fake narration or a spin-off series,

1450
01:23:39,280 --> 01:23:40,715
just as long as I have this.

1451
01:23:40,749 --> 01:23:42,684
[Gintoki] Oh, you're wrapping things up?

1452
01:23:42,717 --> 01:23:44,352
Okay, you get one minute.

1453
01:23:44,686 --> 01:23:47,155
[ominous music]

1454
01:23:47,188 --> 01:23:50,458
[Sogo] Things went back to how they used to be. Alas!

1455
01:23:50,692 --> 01:23:53,528
That only signaled the start of a new battle

1456
01:23:53,561 --> 01:23:54,829
for the Shinsengumi.

1457
01:23:54,863 --> 01:23:56,564
[music continues]

1458
01:23:56,598 --> 01:23:59,401
Forget the ending, we're getting a new damn preview!

1459
01:23:59,434 --> 01:24:02,570
[Sogo] What is the Shinsengumi's new battle? You ask.

1460
01:24:02,604 --> 01:24:03,872
Who is their new foe?

1461
01:24:03,905 --> 01:24:06,341
[Gintoki] He's not new at all! We saw him earlier!

1462
01:24:06,374 --> 01:24:08,676
[Sogo] What is the Shinsengumi's new weapon?

1463
01:24:08,710 --> 01:24:10,412
[Gintoki] Hey, what happened to blandy?

1464
01:24:12,847 --> 01:24:16,151
