1491
01:25:17,745 --> 01:25:19,581
This is the end, just take it easy.

1492
01:25:19,614 --> 01:25:21,749
There is no end to the duty of the police, okay!

1493
01:25:21,783 --> 01:25:23,418
- [Kyubei] Is that so? - [ominous music]

1494
01:25:23,451 --> 01:25:25,487
