1502
01:25:42,837 --> 01:25:45,273
When I invited her to come visit with everyone,

1503
01:25:45,306 --> 01:25:46,941
she insisted on helping out.

1504
01:25:46,975 --> 01:25:48,643
I came up with a way where I could

1505
01:25:48,676 --> 01:25:50,678
serve men without approaching them.

1506
01:25:50,712 --> 01:25:52,747
