1512
01:26:03,458 --> 01:26:04,859
Huh! So predictable.

1513
01:26:09,297 --> 01:26:11,299
That's is. Cleanup's complete.

1514
01:26:11,332 --> 01:26:13,735
[Gintoki] Forget hard-to-get, this is down right dangerous.

1515
01:26:15,470 --> 01:26:16,905
Gin, you can't...

1516
01:26:16,938 --> 01:26:20,241
[Gintoki] What in the name of all that is holy is she doing?

1517
01:26:20,475 --> 01:26:23,378
What's up? I came here to hang out like you asked me to

1518
01:26:23,411 --> 01:26:25,413
