1521
01:26:28,883 --> 01:26:30,585
Tsuki! Kyubei! Hi.

1522
01:26:30,618 --> 01:26:31,819
Kagura.

1523
01:26:31,853 --> 01:26:33,821
- I hope you've been well. - Mm-hm.

1524
01:26:34,355 --> 01:26:35,957
I didn't know you guys were here.

1525
01:26:35,990 --> 01:26:37,959
