1528
01:26:43,765 --> 01:26:47,435
They just wanna be in the spotlight of the big finale.

1529
01:26:47,835 --> 01:26:48,970
But now, we can wrap up

1530
01:26:49,003 --> 01:26:51,639
- all their stories in the narration. - [shouting]

1531
01:26:52,040 --> 01:26:54,008
