01:27:15,396 --> 01:27:17,632
Want me to list all of the Dragon Ball's

1541
01:27:17,665 --> 01:27:19,968
adversaries to prove it, I can do it!

1542
01:27:20,001 --> 01:27:21,469
[Shinpachi] Just by saying that, you've only proven

1543
01:27:21,502 --> 01:27:22,670
that you're wasted!

